  <h1>POS Systems for Maine Dispensaries: What You Need in 2026</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">A complete guide to point-of-sale systems in Maine's cannabis market</p>
</div>

<section class="fact-box">
  <h2>Maine POS Requirements at a Glance</h2>
  <table aria-label="Maine cannabis POS requirements">
